{"tid":675061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱推「一周一行」後內地客量跌四成　邱騰華：北區水貨客情況已改善","createTime":"2018-05-23T08:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T10:58:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a15384f885d2a874e5454ad49be0dfc60dd933a","tid":675061,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180523/s00001/784c3201c7bb50e3e2b9f02fccba3b7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180523%2Fs00001%2F784c3201c7bb50e3e2b9f02fccba3b7f.jpg&h=9278a398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華回應立法會議員質詢時表示，自從調整深圳戶籍居民「一簽多行」至「一周一行」後，內地旅客已由2014年最高峰時1400多萬人次，降至去年876萬，減幅達四成，認為政策成效顯著，暫時無意改變。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華補充，內地流行網購，已經較少人會在同一地點大量購買同一種類物品。他同意現時北區水貨客情況仍有改善之處，但強調確實已經有改善，當局將繼續與執法部門緊密聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n議員廖長江關注內地旅客迫爆露營地點，問政府會否考慮調控旅客數目。邱騰華只稱，有留意旅客來港露營情況，當局已即時跟進，亦得悉部分露營地點有登記制度，或讓港人優先使用。<br />\n<br />\n他另外提到，訪港旅客人數去年起止跌回升，政府將在旅遊高峰期前召開跨部門會議，商討應對人潮，例如食環署保持各區公廁清潔，警方加派人手維持通道暢通、確保公眾秩序等。<br />\n<br />\n邱並說，根據過往檔期顯示，近年旅客秩序有改善，當局亦樂意研究，應否擴展九龍城區旅遊大使計劃至其他地區，為旅客提供適切協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180523/s00001/1527062725668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180523%2Fs00001%2F1527062725668&d=c%2BJMtgH2msu1T9K6ZL12a7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c67eb1b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180523%2Fs00001%2F1527062725668&h=5709dc19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180523/s00001/1527062725668</a>"},{"pid":"ade141468ab663b44d0eca47cb118efb32359448","tid":675061,"uid":23236,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦，改善左喺條撚度呀？成街都仲係喼，成街都仲係水貨舖！"},{"pid":"f2db11cbe15a05f36bfc1f61546a1023d1adf510","tid":675061,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"立法強制要求一眾高官只可居住上水直至離任"},{"pid":"ab3ee9f4ee352650395c818f1f12032485b31b15","tid":675061,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"佢每日過關睇下人有無少? 唔過關搭下東鐵線先鳩UP. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37779ce11b70c1dd6e546bd17fc06e5d2ca9d32","tid":675061,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"又試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d946eeb238222f95f164dd036ca79ef2e7601f6f","tid":675061,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"非法露營喎...."},{"pid":"74294dd055377dd4d2aac3f967dde33817eaa3c5","tid":675061,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"睇下sogo門口先啦仆街。"},{"pid":"4050935de96e6548ca7a48cfd1079b188800eec2","tid":675061,"uid":41501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:30:33.000Z","msg":"你嚟上水同我行返轉先好講，平日都多人到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n六日我覺得唔只冇少，可能仲多左"},{"pid":"8aeed7a367ddaaec02b348b6b2134089f34f585f","tid":675061,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"改善？邊度改善？<br />\n<br />\n睇過睇過"},{"pid":"668b6c99700870e7378f1142d883202f859b18b3","tid":675061,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"過嚟上水住返三五七年先好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125af7f5b73cac0b354ce8f2b4b7415ace4b9cac","tid":675061,"uid":72058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1459c9d8b57e4c1081c07a4bbd3093a5a41b41d7","tid":675061,"uid":54633,"like":0,"dislike":